**6. MASS BALANCE --- S1 INPUT → OUTPUT**

All C:N ratios are formula-driven (DM-weighted). Never hardcode a
blended C:N. Always use the N conversion factor 4.67 (not 6.25).

**6.1 EFB Stream Balance**

  --------------------------------------------------------------------------
