**10. NPK RELAY TO NPK CALCULATOR**

At the end of every S1 run, the following NPK data packet must be sent
to the CFI NPK Value Dashboard / Calculator. This is a hard requirement
--- no phase completes without NPK relay confirmation.

  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **NPK            **S1 Output  **Units**   **Derivation / Source**
  Parameter**      Value**                  
  ---------------- ------------ ----------- -----------------------------------
  N --- EFB        340 kg/day   kg N/day    EFB DM × N% DM (0.76% N ÷ N-factor
  contribution                              4.67 = 0.163% N; 120.8 t DM/day ×
                                            0.163% → \~197 kg ... \[recalc per
                                            run\]

  N --- OPDC       140 kg/day   kg N/day    OPDC DM × 2.3% N
  contribution                              

  N --- POS        \~83 kg/day  kg N/day    POS DM × 1.76% N
  contribution                              

  TOTAL N          \~582 kg/day kg N/day    Guardrail baseline --- recalculate
  (3-stream)                                per actual S1 outputs

  P --- EFB        47 kg/day    kg P/day    EFB DM × P% from S0 lab

  P --- OPDC       126 kg/day   kg P/day    OPDC DM × P% from S0 lab

  P --- POS        \~24 kg/day  kg P/day    POS DM × P% from S0 lab

  TOTAL P          \~197 kg/day kg P/day    Guardrail baseline
  (3-stream)                                

  K --- total      \~930 kg/day kg K/day    Guardrail baseline --- breakdown
  (3-stream)                                per S0 lab

  NPK value basis  Urea \$350/t ---         Standard pricing
                   │ TSP                    
                   \$450/t │                
                   MOP \$380/t              

  N replacement    \$1.50/kg N  USD/kg      Sinar Mas estate actual
  price (estate)                            

  P replacement    \$1.80/kg    USD/kg      Sinar Mas estate actual
  price (estate)   P₂O₅                     

  K replacement    \$0.90/kg    USD/kg      Sinar Mas estate actual
  price (estate)   K₂O                      
  -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

NPK relay is written to the s1_run_log.npk_relay columns AND sent as a
trigger to the NPK Value Dashboard via Supabase real-time subscription
or Zapier webhook, whichever is configured at the time of run.

> **⚠ NPK RELAY IS MANDATORY. If N, P, or K data is unavailable (DATA
> GAP) at end of S1 run, log the data gap explicitly and use guardrail
> baseline values as the relay placeholder. Never relay zero.**

