S2 Chemical Treatment (PKSA alkaline pre-treatment) requires the
following confirmed parameters from S1 before commencing. S1 Calculator
writes these to the s2_payload JSONB column and raises a status flag =
\'S1_COMPLETE\' in Supabase.

  --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  **Parameter      **Source in    **Guardrail Gate**   **If NOT met**
  Required by S2** S1**                                
  ---------------- -------------- -------------------- ---------------------------
  EFB particle     EVS-01 screen  HARD GATE --- must   Return to EHM-01, remill
  size ≤2 mm D90   verified       pass                 

  EFB MC ≤45%      Post-press     HARD GATE            Additional press pass or
                   moisture check                      reject

  OPDC MC ≤40%     Post-press     HARD GATE --- pore   HOLD batch, do not advance
  (floor)          moisture check damage risk          to S2

  POS MC ≤65%      Post-dewater   Hard gate            Additional dewater pass
                   check                               

  Fe mg/kg DM      ICP-OES        Gates POS inclusion  Restrict inclusion rate per
  (POS)            package A      rate                 Fe band
                                  (CFI-LAB-POME-001)   

  PKSA dose        S2 calculates  6--10 kg PKSA/t      S1 provides blend
  requirement      from blend CP, substrate │ pH       composition only
                   lignin, C:N    target 10--12        

  Lab analysis tag S1 lab         3-day replicate      Provisional tag used ---
  (S1-LAB-xxxx)    analysis       confirmed            flag as unconfirmed
                   packet issued                       

  OPDC yield       Mass balance   LOCKED --- never     Investigate press settings
  verified at      check at press change               if deviation \>5%
  15.2% of EFB FW  discharge                           
  --------------------------------------------------------------------------------

