**15. AI SEARCH INTEGRATION (PROMPT 8)**

The AI Search agent runs every 3 days to update the following
S1-relevant datasets. All external search results are appended (never
overwrite) with source, date, and uncertainty flags. Only Tier A--C
sources are accepted (see RESEARCH-INTENSITY prompt).

-   Indonesian OEM equipment pricing: screw presses, hammer mills,
    trommel screens, decanters

-   Press dewatering performance data for EFB and OPDC --- moisture
    reduction curves vs. press pressure

-   Particle size effects on BSF colonisation and microbial inoculation
    uptake (S3 relevance)

-   PLN electricity tariff updates (current: \$0.091437/kWh baseline
    IDR/USD 15,800)

-   Indonesian construction cost indices for industrial buildings
    (benchmark: \$185/m² PEB)

-   Press cake nutrient analysis from peer-reviewed sources --- verify
    against CFI canonical values

> **⚠ ANTI-HALLUCINATION RULE: No equipment price, efficiency value, or
> mass-balance coefficient may be inserted from an external search
> result without: (1) author/org, (2) year, (3) title/source, (4) unit
> verification. DATA GAP is always preferred over a fabricated value.**

